manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: THE 4-SECRETS DRIVING THE COMPETITION CRAZY! 1. It all started one day when I bought a shiny new phone. I didn’t want to lose that smooth look with a clunky embarrassing case. Yes…I went NAKED! You guessed it, case free. A week later, my phone turned to a shattered mess when it slipped out of my hand. 2. I was SOOO upset with myself! Being a careful person with a firm grip in the hand, I convinced myself I’ll beat the odds. BIG MISTAKE! However, I was still against the infinite cases missing impact protection or the big bulky monsters I couldn’t stand… 3. The pain and suffering was too great. I called together my designers and engineers into the highly secret Crave R&D LAB. We discovered MILLIONS of people just like you needed a solution. So we decided we were going to fix this problem once and for all. 4. After many sleepless nights in the lab we birthed the Crave Dual Guard. We figured out how to offer unparalleled super impact protection while delivering a beautiful design. 1 million+ only trust Crave in keeping your phone safe. DON’T DELAY, SHIP TODAY!

Samsung S21 - Dual Guard Series The perfect balance of protection and style for your S21 begins with the Crave Dual Guard. Keeping your phone in perfectly working order can be difficult when you have a habit of dropping your phone or letting your kids play with it at dinner. Either way, you’re just asking to use the protection plan and get a refurbished phone in its place. That’s why you need to keep it from ever getting that far with ultimate protection from the Crave Dual Guard Case designed for the Samsung Galaxy S21. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect fit, grip and protection
reviews.reviewText: I choose a Crave Dual Guard anytime I get a new phone. I had passed my old iPhone w/this kind of case down to my teenage sin who left it in the middle of our cul de sac overnight (!?!). Found the phone the next morning in the gutter. It clearly had been driven over because the corners of the case had cracked off. The phone itself somehow had no damage at all!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Comfortable case, not bulky at all, love the colors
reviews.reviewText: I love these cases so much, they are exactly what I wanted; they aren't heavy, the colors are great, fairly sleek, and they provide proper protection. I have dropped my phone several times, even on pavement or asphalt, and my phone screen is yet to crack because of this case. I am a fan of the texture of the case, my phone doesn't slide around and it is easy to hold. The durability is pretty good, the green case I had had snapped near where the camera is, however it remained functional, I decided to get a second case just because I like this brand as well as the design and color selection. I plan on buying more of them just to have cases to mix and match the inner case and outer shell.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I had killed my phone case and needed a quick replacement. This case is perfect! It has metal side button covers so they work easily and came in the proper size for my phone while looking stylish! Love it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fits well, grips well
reviews.reviewText: I've had my Crave case for a couple weeks now. I love the forest green color and the texture on the case as it doesn't slip out of my hand like others have. It does slide into my pocket easily and has done a good job protecting my phone the times I have dropped it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Lasted a few months but..
reviews.reviewText: The case kind of looked cool and lasted about 3 months but the plastic shell that is laid over the rubber base is pretty brittle. I think I had dropped it a total of 2 or 3 times and the red plastic shell had completely chipped away at the top wright near the camera. After this happened the outter shell wouldnt stay secured and I had decided to just throw it all away. Im not sure why so many positive reviews but okie doke. I dont usually leave any reviews on anything that I buy but maybe this could help you. Im sure there are better and more sturdy cases out there.
